Title : Congenital temporomandibular joint ankylosis: clinical characterization and natural history of four unrelated affected individuals.
Date : 2005
Publication_type : Journal Article
Abstract : The objective of this study was to describe four unrelated patients affected by congenital temporomandibular joint ankylosis. Clinical delineation, natural history, and possible etiologies are discussed. Clinical aspects that are important for follow-up are outlined.
